{"id": "1491421003828432902", "channel_id": "1431211464324157450", "type": 0, "author_id": "1425265631078645841", "author_name": "megane0965_78083", "author_bot": false, "content": "この前もアドバイスいただきましたが、速攻型のリリニムパ模索してます。\n\nこれまでは死亡抵抗ゼロが普通の守りの毒パだったんですけど、それだとリリニムオルライカーでもカーシアステージ15ターンがせいぜいで…。\n\n毒パと相性良いカエクス・カレンのステージにあたりつけてステージ構成まとめるかな…", "timestamp": "2026-04-08T12:54:36.575000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431211464324157450", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "リリーさんの構成(毒パ)について", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1491421393013969086", "channel_id": "1431211464324157450", "type": 0, "author_id": "1425265631078645841", "author_name": "megane0965_78083", "author_bot": false, "content": "あとやっぱり時計完凸も必要そうなので、リリニムで8,800目指すのは最低一ヶ月かかりそうです", "timestamp": "2026-04-08T12:56:09.364000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431211464324157450", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "リリーさんの構成(毒パ)について", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1491422490017398947", "channel_id": "1431211464324157450", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "リリニムミリ24の海の祭りとか", "timestamp": "2026-04-08T13:00:30.910000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431211464324157450", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "リリーさんの構成(毒パ)について", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1491422838278852759", "channel_id": "1431211464324157450", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "鍵はトゥル札だと思うんですよね", "timestamp": "2026-04-08T13:01:53.942000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431211464324157450", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "リリーさんの構成(毒パ)について", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1491428759935647745", "channel_id": "1431211464324157450", "type": 0, "author_id": "1425265631078645841", "author_name": "megane0965_78083", "author_bot": false, "content": "ミリいなくても海の祭り結構良かったし、その構成が良いかもしれないですね…。\n\nトゥル餅リセットしちゃってないんですよね…。ミストレアさんのまねなんですが、入学の日で商店で105狂気稼いじゃうのもありですかね。", "timestamp": "2026-04-08T13:25:25.775000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431211464324157450", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "リリーさんの構成(毒パ)について", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1491429676894257273", "channel_id": "1431211464324157450", "type": 0, "author_id": "1425265631078645841", "author_name": "megane0965_78083", "author_bot": false, "content": "よく見たら蚊取り線香みたいなの三つありました", "timestamp": "2026-04-08T13:29:04.395000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431211464324157450", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "リリーさんの構成(毒パ)について", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1491431414757982229", "channel_id": "1431211464324157450", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "お", "timestamp": "2026-04-08T13:35:58.734000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431211464324157450", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "リリーさんの構成(毒パ)について", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
