{"id": "1491433733184688230", "channel_id": "1431211464324157450", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "あれ割と最適だと思いますー", "timestamp": "2026-04-08T13:45:11.490000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431211464324157450", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "リリーさんの構成(毒パ)について", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1491433885211299913", "channel_id": "1431211464324157450", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "マフィ札はメインキーチャで狂気盛り出来るので、ちょっと弱めのアクートみたいに使えます", "timestamp": "2026-04-08T13:45:47.736000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👈", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431211464324157450", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "リリーさんの構成(毒パ)について", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1491439166351867904", "channel_id": "1431211464324157450", "type": 0, "author_id": "1425265631078645841", "author_name": "megane0965_78083", "author_bot": false, "content": "あ、でもライムさんリリー餅完凸か…悩むー", "timestamp": "2026-04-08T14:06:46.858000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431211464324157450", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "リリーさんの構成(毒パ)について", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
